snippet.title: AMBER ALERT‼️ Brizz Rawsteen Has Been Missing Since Brawl👊🏽 With Murda Mook
snippet.description:
Brizz Rawsteen was last seen on stage for the main event for Darklyfe vs Murdaland. A short series of events on stage erupted a huge brawl involving several battle rappers. Brizz and other Cavegang members got into it with Murda Mook, Calicoe and other Dot Mobb members. Since then we have not heard much from Brizz. But with the rumored anniversary card approaching in December, will he make an appearance? And against who?

Follow me on IG @everyotherbar
